findStrings.find: SELECT `car_details`.`car_model`,`car_details`.`seater`,`price_info`.`price`,`scrap`.`fname`,`scrap`.`lname`,`car_details`.`regno`,`user`.`fname`,`user`.`lname` FROM `car_details` JOIN `scraprequest` ON `scraprequest`.`carid`=`car_details`.`id` JOIN `scrap` ON `scrap`.`lid`=`scraprequest`.`lid` JOIN `price_info` ON `price_info`.`reqid`=`scraprequest`.`id` JOIN `user` ON `user`.`lid`=`car_details`.`lid` WHERE `scraprequest`.`id`=
